3.1.name: wordpress/design-approval-system
3.1.description:
NEW: Approved designs now get a STAR on the Project Board, and Clients signature is recorded to the database. Check out the Project Board. Clients, projects, & designs are organized on one page + Clients can login to see there designs! View Live Example.
